          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1666180377657-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into <strong>chips</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chips</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1666180381240-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1666180381240-x400.jpg",
