          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1666180381240-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong>, then cut into rectangles for per person and add them to a separate baking tray lined with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>red onion chutney</strong> to the centre of the pastry rectangles,<strong> </strong>lengthways, then top with the <strong>goats cheese, spinach & butternut squash filling</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1666180384104-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1666180384104-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1666180384104-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1666180384104-x1000.jpg",
